dct_description_sm: Map shows the Spanish provinces of Granada and Murcia, with part of North Africa; relief shown pictorially. Dutch text on verso with caption title: Het koningrijck Granaden; p. 13; signature M. Probably issued in: Toonneel des aerdrycx, oft Nieuwe atlas / uytgegeven door Wilhelm en Iohannem Blaeu. t'Amsterdam : by Johan Blaeu, [1647]-1650.
